fields.name: Snorkeling Mask Optical Corrective Lenses - MK245 RX
fields.description:
Promate Scope Prescription Scuba Dive Snorkeling Mask Optical Corrective Lenses - MK245 RX
Promate Scope Prescription Dive Mask (MK245 RX)
* Ideal for smaller to medium faces (fits almost everyone)
* Face seal size: 4 1/2" width by  3 3/8" inches height
* Crystal, liquid silicone injected skirt and strap
* Double edge comfort seal
* Ultra low volume
* Broad peripheral view
* High quality 
* Tempered glass lenses
* Optical lenses available from –1.0 to –10.0 by increments of 0.5 (for nearsighted or myopia)
* Optical lenses available from +1.0 to +4.5 by increments of 0.5 (for farsighted or hyperopia)
* Bifocal / Gauge Reader lenses available from +1.0 to +4.0 by increments of 0.5. (top plain without prescription, bottom with magnifier reader)

fields.name: Promate Binar Blade Scuba Dive Fins
fields.description:
*Efficient, fast and for easy kicking. The Binar Blade fins use two materials in the blade, directing the water flow for maximum kicking efficiency. The innovative open heel fins, with dual channels, are for 
optimizing water flow. A unique design that allows water exiting located in front of the foot pocket by eliminating resistance during fining. 
*EVA fins blade, TPR foot pocket, TPR channels convey greater power with reduced effort, Patented quick-release fin buckles 
*Men's Size (Shoes): S(4-6), M(6-9), L(9-11), XL(11-13) 
Women's Size (Shoes): S
